---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Builder. Writer. Systems thinker.">
  <section class="container-narrow py-16 md:py-24">
    <!-- Hero: Image + Name + What I Do -->
    <header class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="w-56 h-56 md:w-72 md:h-72 rounded-full border-4 border-os-accent shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
          <img 
            src="/personal-os/images/bhaskar.png" 
            alt="Bhaskar Kotakonda" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            style="transform: scale(1.8) translateX(5%) translateY(-5%);"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4">
            Bhaskar Kotakonda
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-os-dark mb-3 max-w-lg">
            I build economically optimal AI infra and systems at hyperscale
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-os-muted">
            Currently: exploring AI workloads, agentic SWE and knowledge management systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- About -->
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-os-dark leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I am a product manager at Microsoft working on the Hardware Platform for Azure Storage. 
        My primary responsibility is to build economically efficient systems across product lines 
        that optimize for performance and customer requirements.
      </p>
      <p>
        My work spans distributed systems, storage optimization, and the intersection of 
        AI workloads with infrastructure. I care deeply about first-principles thinking, 
        writing clearly, and building things that last.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
